title: Antonio Brown, Kyler Murray rumors with Jason La Canfora (Football 3/7)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by CBS Sports NFL Insider Jason La Canfora to break down the latest news and notes surrounding the NFL, including the rumors about Kyler Murray going No. 1 overall to the Cardinals or a possible trade AND the possibility of Antonio Brown being traded with a deadline looming this Friday.
